body: https://cmssdt.cern.ch/jenkins/view/All/job/update-cmssw-l2-histroy/ fails as it can not apply the changes between 77b24b08456dcc8d243f43f3bc83abf98e7ff9cf and last cms-bot commit. As `categories.py` is not changes during this time, so we just update the last process commit to head of cms-bot. This avoid the merge conflicts . Also as we only need the last process commit so this Pr also cleans up all old process commits
title: update last processed commit; remove old processed commits
